{"tid":1023371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人另一伴有情緒病架？","createTime":"2019-02-15T17:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T17:03:36.000Z","uid":145585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54105d48b2242d46296681435fed1c6bce30af5d","tid":1023371,"uid":145585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"我另一伴有呢病，聽佢講都有一段日子，時好時壞咁。咁我作為佢另一伴，我好想幫佢，因為我愛佢，好想可以令到佢無事好返哂，唔想再受呢個病困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問如果有呢種病嘅人唔開心嘅話，可以點幫佢地？或者要講啲咩說話先會令到佢地心情會好啲？<br />\n因為個病會令到佢，無原無故突然好難過好失落，我又唔知點解會咁，我仲以為係我做錯事令到佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求各位大神指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好愛佢，所以好想佢快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d330dc8b8d86bc9c6f437b9946b9ff5fbbd6d5","tid":1023371,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d214d860242be8bc4532f51ff9aee358123e47eb","tid":1023371,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦on9"},{"pid":"150bb164f7a703863dbec4217a2cf374ed06fc23","tid":1023371,"uid":51212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"有，啱啱仲分咗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}